casebody.data:
Nos. 20 and 21,

Misc.

Lober et al. v. Morgan, Lewis & Bockius et al. October 22, 1945. Mr. Archibald Palmer for petitioners. Messrs. Frederic L. Ballard and Allen Hunter White for Ballard, Spahr, Andrews & Ingersoll et al., Mr. Henry 8. Drinker for Drinker, Biddle & Reath et al., and Acting Solicitor General Judson, Messrs. Roger S. Foster, Milton V. Freeman and George Zolotar for the Securities & Exchange Commission, respondents.

The motion for leave to file petition for writs of certiorari is denied. Mr. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
